class Solution {
    public boolean isPowerOfThree(int n) {
        if (n <= 0) {
            return false;
        }
        double logValue = Math.log10(n) / Math.log10(3);
        return Math.abs(logValue - Math.floor(logValue)) < Double.MIN_VALUE;
    }
}
```

Here's how this solution works:

